Detailed Description

The base class for boolean config managed variables. Inherits from RTRManagedBoolean and provides services for specifying configuration and default values for the boolean variable.

Consumers can modify the variable if permitted by the publisher (modifyEnabled == RTRTRUE). Permission is granted/denied when the variable is created and cannot be changed during its life-cycle. The context (Managed Object) is notified of changes.

This class cannot be directly instantiated.
